parameters:
It looks like a crystal for teleportation. It says Still under
preparation.

The transfer crystal is shining... Will you move to the
teleportation space?

\SE[2]Oh... I've heard about it, but... \SE[1]It really is a
city, huh... Ulyssean is...

\SE[15] How about Lunaroa? Are you enjoying the hustle and bustle
of the city?

\SE[21]That's great. You have to quickly get used to the new
environment, you know. \SE[45]It may be troublesome, but it's
better to enjoy it.

\SE[37]Well, the biggest issue might be the money... \SE[52]I'm
getting the bare minimum that I need, but it's still tough. I
want to have some play money too, you know...

\SE[32]That won't work if there are no customers...
\!\SE[21]Ulyssean is a proper place, so if we openly advertise,
it might cause some trouble...
\SE[38]Hmm... I see. That's a difficult situation...

\SE[2]Hey, what's wrong, big brother? You look really down.
\SE[1]Did something happen to trouble you?

\SE[33]As immigrants, we don't really have many acquaintances.
\!\SE[15]So, I want to interact with various people and broaden
my horizons.

Immigrants... I see, it must have been tough for you. Compared to
that, my worries are really trivial...

\SE\SE[15]You mentioned it earlier, right? If it's okay with me,
would you like me to listen to your story? \SE[15]Even if it
doesn't lead to a solution, it might help you move forward in
some way.
Huh, um... even if you listen to someone like me...

Well, since you offered, maybe I'll tell you... She seems to be
around the same age as well...

\SE[42]Hmm, so you have someone you like, huh... \SE[16]No,
that's great. It's cute that you have such innocent worries. I
actually quite enjoy hearing about those kinds of stories.

\SE[2]How much interaction do you have with that girl? \SE[51]For
example, like going on dates or something.

Well, to be honest, I've never had a proper conversation with
her. I've only seen her from a distance... But recently, I
started seeing her more often, so I thought maybe she's also an
immigrant like you...

\SE[20]So it's love at first sight, huh? \SE[16]Big brother,
you're surprisingly innocent. [2]I don't dislike that about you.
[3]People like that...
You speak like an uncle or something...

\SE[57]Hmm... But in the end, isn't the only option to make a
move? \SE[2]Cute girls always end up being snatched away by
someone else, so it's easier to have a quick answer. For both of
us.

\SE[16]And you know, sometimes if you confess with a lot of
momentum, they might just go along with it and say okay.
\SE[0]It's also hard to refuse if they feel guilty about it.

\SE[46]There's no cheating or unfairness in love. \SE[0]If you
just start dating for now, then it's yours. [2]In the end, if the
two of you like each other, isn't that enough? [3]Afterwards, you
can slowly become mutual lovers and make each other happy, right?

You're right... Your way of thinking might have some truth to
it...

\SE[21] (Ahaha, sorry. I just really like talking about love... I
ended up rambling.)
\SE[15] (Sorry. Just a little bit more, okay?)

\SE[2]By the way, what's the name of the girl you like?
\!\SE[5]If it's okay with me, I'd like to support you in a good
way...

I don't know her name... She's probably a little younger than
you...

Her hair is purple... She has a quiet demeanor. But in reality,
she seems to be a bit more cheerful...

\SE[43] Purple hair and seems quiet... But actually quite
cheerful...?

Also... I seem to have trouble speaking well. Aphasia... is that
what it's called? I think there must have been something in my
past...

Even those aspects... are cute. Like a doll. I want to marry
her... and create children together... I want to spend my whole
life for her...!

\SE[21] (No, I stepped on a landmine here... \!\SE[0] Let's run
away. Before it becomes troublesome.)

\SE[9]Ah, we should probably go soon. \SE[39]There's a curfew,
you know. Curfew.
Curfew...? It's still early afternoon though...
Ah, to meet in a place like this... Ah, truly adorable...!!!

Ah, as expected... this innocence... this pitiful clumsiness...!
Yet, this alluring body...! Everything is my ideal!!

Ah, there's a nice scent...! I knew it, I've fallen in love with
you...

I got it... Let's put that girl's advice into practice. Let's
push through with momentum. That's right...

I 'love you'...! Please date me with the intention of getting
married!! Please, I'm counting on you!!!

I did it! I got her okay!! With this, we can get married...!
Let's build a happy family together!!

\SE[39] Alright, alright, let's stop here... You shouldn't be so
rough with girls, you know. \SE[57] Oh no, I went and talked to a
dangerous person...

W-Why are you getting in the way...!! Y-You were supposed to
understand me...!
\SE[39]Even though it's because of my careless advice... *sigh*
T-This... I'm being rejected...? I can't marry this girl...?

\SE[2]Yeah, it's really unfortunate. \SE[5]...Ronoa. Maybe I
should tell you this.

Physically repulsive!!!? It's over!! He's the most hopeless
guy...!! He doesn't have even a millimeter of possibility!!

It's over... There's no reason for me to live like this...
Tomorrow, I'll go bury myself in the Motterel Mine...

\SE[7] (Oh no... I'm feeling down. \!\SE[38] It would be really
troublesome if he actually died, so what should I do...)

I wanted to marry such a cute girl... Before I die, I wanted to
have sex with such a cute girl and lose my virginity...

\SE\SE[25]Ah, then should we just do ecchi instead? \SE[25]If
it's no kissing, no intercourse, and 50,000 yen for a separate
room, depending on the options, we can discuss it.

\SE\SE[0]No, we're aiming to be pros, right? We have to be able
to handle any opponent. \SE[0]So, what do we do?

Y-You're saying that I can pay you money to do ecchi with me...?
Um, how much is the fee...?

\SE[34]You said 50,000 for a separate room, right? It means the
hotel fee and 50,000G. \SE[45]So, I'll let you have some butt
play.

I-It's really tough... B-But if it's just that... I'll somehow
manage...

\SE[16]Alright, the deal is done. Shall we take a break at the
inn then? \SE[1]Let's go, Ronoa.

These blocks here are called bouncing stones. Hey, would you like
to try a jump too, miss?

I heard that the amazing jumper can perform the legendary 4th
jump. Do you know what that means, big sister?

I wonder how many times I can jump today! Damn it... I'm getting
addicted to it...!

Ulyssean Swordsmanship ~ Beginners Welcome ~ Dojo Invaders also
Welcome!

This kind of jump... it doesn't have any meaning, but... for some
reason, I just can't help but do it...

I am guarding the castle gate. Please leave if you have no
business here.

The torch next to me is so hot... I feel like I'm turning into a
steamed octopus inside this armor...

Are you here for official business within the castle? I'm sorry,
but please leave.

The water here is purified, so it's clean. You can drink it if
you want, but it's better to avoid it.

Today is a wonderful day... The flowers are blooming. The birds
are chirping...

This is the Adventurer's Guild. It's best to receive quest
requests here.

I made this goddess statue 10 years ago... but now I'm concerned
about the sculpting. Could you let me shave off just a little bit
of the cheeks...?
